  "title": "Create Logistics",
  "description": "More compact than a vault, organize your inventory with an Item Silo",
  "body": "![](https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1013/185/create_logistics_banner.png)\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p>Here is my Create Logistics addon. Currently, it only adds a single item: the Item Silo. This is a box that looks like a toolbox, but it can hold only one type of item in quantities over 3,200. Like a bundle, it can be used directly from your inventory to enhance storage and ease of use. It can also be handy during crafting, as it allows you to store significantly more than a standard bundle in a single slot.</p></div></div></div></div>\n\n<div><div><div>I'm French and&nbsp;this mod was done with Mcreator</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1013/173/item_silo_1.gif\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1013/175/item_silo_3.gif\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1013/181/item_silo_4-1.gif\" width=\"640\" height=\"130\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1013/174/item_silo_2.gif\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1013/178/item_silo_5.gif\"></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>",
